  </datafield>
  <datafield tag="246" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
    <subfield code="a">Simulations of Stellar Core Collapse, Bounce, and Postbounce Evolution with Boltzmann Neutrino Transport, and Implications for the Core Collapse Supernova Mechanism</subfield>
    <subfield code="9">arXiv</subfield>
